# ===== Minimal shell customization =====

# Short hostname for prompt (first part of the machine name)
HOSTNAME_SHORT=${HOST%%.*}

# Prompt: blue username@host, white current dir, blue arrow
PROMPT="%F{blue}%n@${HOSTNAME_SHORT}%f %F{white}%1~ %F{blue}â†’ %f "

# Useful aliases
